anxiety...

00:31:01.492 --> 00:31:03.154
depression...

00:31:05.496 --> 00:31:07.294
poor learning...

00:31:08.299 --> 00:31:10.859
obesity and even cancers.

00:31:11.603 --> 00:31:14.538
They can change
the course of a child's life.

00:31:18.209 --> 00:31:20.411
a growing number
of scientists,

00:31:20.411 --> 00:31:23.779
the implications
of these findings are clear.

